1. use the hadoop CLI to compile the Recomender.java file
       hadoop com.sun.tools.javac.Main Recomender.java

2. build a jar file (you can find one in 'jar' folder)
       jar cf recomender.jar Recomender*.class

3. the input files are in the 'input/' folder

4. make sur there is no 'output' folder

5. run the application
       hadoop jar recomender.jar Recomender input/ output

6. see the result in the 'output/part-r-00000' file you should obtain the same
result as in 'old_output/part-r-00000'
